review_blob:
A rich tasty pale ale with a shady character and some yeast in the beverage but without messing things up. Im a new fan of pale ale but an old fan of Peter Carlsson och Bl Grodorna.  Having one of these is a grand treat but it is sadly pretty hard to find, if you get a chance and like this kind of beer than buy yourself a bottle and enjoy it. 

Its a great treat in a bottle

A wonderful pale ale, wonderful and tasty. This really is a great beer that has that extra sting in its taste that common beer lacks and if you want to try something extra ordinary than I suggest you get yourself a bottle of this brew
